import React, { Component } from 'react'
import Calendar from 'react-calendar'
// import { formatDate } from 'react-calendar/dist/cjs/shared/dateFormatter'
import Reservations from '../components/Reservations'


class Second extends Component {

  data = [
    {date:"2023-10-13",
      name:"Denis",
      phone: "8402847493020",
      time: "10:30"},
      {date:"2023-11-13",
      name:"Denis",
      phone: "8402847493020",
      time: "10:30",
      count_person: 5},

      {date:"2023-10-13",
      name:"JOHN",
      phone: "8402847493020",
      time: "10:30"},
      {date:"2023-11-13",
      name:"Denis",
      phone: "8402847493020",
      time: "23:30",
      count_person: 2},

      {date:"2023-11-13",
      name:"Denis",
      phone: "8402847493020",
      time: "10:30"},
      {date:"2023-11-13",
      name:"Denis",
      phone: "8402847493020",
      time: "10:30",
      count_person: 5}
  ]

  render() {

    return (
      <>
        <main>
          <Reservations users={this.data}/>
        </main>

        <aside>
          <Calendar onChange={this.normal_data} />
        </aside>
      </>
      
    )
  }

  normal_data(el){
    var day = el.getDate();
    var month = el.getMonth();
    var year = el.getFullYear();

    var normal_data = year+"-"+month+"-"+day

    console.log(normal_data)
  }
}

export default Second
